name: COMMONWEALTH of Pennsylvania, Respondent v. Anthony WASHINGTON, Petitioner

parties: COMMONWEALTH of Pennsylvania, Respondent v. Anthony WASHINGTON, Petitioner.

opinions.text:
ORDER
PER CURIAM.
AND NOW, this 28th day of April, 2009, the Petition for Leave to File Petition for Allowance of Appeal Nunc Pro Tunc is GRANTED. Petitioner’s counsel is directed to file a Petition for Allowance of Appeal within 30 days of this order.
opinions.author: PER CURIAM.

casebody.head_matter:
COMMONWEALTH of Pennsylvania, Respondent v. Anthony WASHINGTON, Petitioner.
No. 34 EM 2009.
Supreme Court of Pennsylvania.
April 28, 2009.
